<div class='carouselRow' style='width: 3600px'>
<ul>
<li class='cover' id='bookCover_59545837'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/59545837-tamesis-street"><img alt="Tamesis Street" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1636128813l/59545837._SX98_.jpg" />
