<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/35959168-the-secrets-between-us"><img alt="The Secrets Between Us" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1512685078l/35959168._SY75_.jpg" />
</a>


